        div.container
          .row.start-md
            .col-md-4
              h2.text-subtitle.text-blue.reveal.effect.effect-reveal Brands are demanding transparency with their dollars, and these categories are the most likely to impact spending.
              .strip.blue
              .spacer
              .text-body.effect.effect-reveal
                p.text-blue Proving ROI is a big concern for brands, and their budgets  will flow into solutions that provide ROI transparency. Agencies see fraud and risk transparency concerns as the most likely to impact their media budget allocations.
              .foot-note.blue.effect.effect-fadeIn
                img.foot-note__icon(src="images/question-white.svg")
                p.text-blue When thinking about digital advertising budgets in 2018, please rate how strongly you see each of the following as a threat to increasing investment in digital advertising. (1 = very low or no threat, and 5 = a significant threat) (% based on those who rated 4 or 5 top-2 box).
